Description of problem:
For >20 content views, just 20 are listed. Due to --per-page / --full-results options missing.


Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable):
rubygem-hammer_cli_katello-0.0.4-14.el6sat.noarch


How reproducible:
100%


Steps to Reproduce:
1. Create >20 content views
2. hammer content-view list


Actual results:
Just first 20 CVs are listed


Expected results:
All CVs listed / have --per-page & --full-results options like content-host list or product list.


